_text = "In the years after the breakup, my dad had three kids with this new women. I feel bad saying anything negative about the situation because she truely does make him happy and I do like her.\n\nI just hate the situation. My mom hasn't moved on, and im worried she never will.\n\nThe kid in this memory is my only brother. Everytime I visit im overwhelmed by what reality is now. Time has softened the emotions, but I don’t feel like my dad’s daughter anymore. The age gap between me and his now youngest daughters is 20 years. When I visit I can’t help but feel a loss of connection as they take up his entire focus.\n\nI can’t blame them though. I've been absent for far too long. My life here has kept me away for too long. Maybe i've done more damage than I've realized."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, DenmonIslandMemory, DenmonIslandMemory, false)
